---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="SocialProof vs Fera.ai — Social proof tools compared | SocialProof" description="Fera.ai starts at $9/mo for Shopify social proof with order counters and review widgets. SocialProof is free to start — simple testimonial collection for any business." canonical="https://socialproof.dev/vs/fera">
<style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; margin: 0; background: #fff; color: #111; }
    nav { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 1rem 2rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; }
    nav a.logo { font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.25rem; color: #111; text-decoration: none; }
    nav .nav-links a { margin-left: 1.5rem; color: #555; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    nav .cta-nav { background: #111; color: #fff !important; padding: .45rem 1rem; border-radius: 6px; }
    .hero { text-align: center; padding: 4rem 2rem 2rem; max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .vs-badge { display: inline-block; background: #f0f0f0; color: #555; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .06em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: .35rem .75rem; border-radius: 99px; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.15; margin: 0 0 1rem; }
    .hero h1 span { color: #4f46e5; }
    .hero p { font-size: 1.15rem; color: #444; max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; }
    .hero-cta { display: inline-block; background: #4f46e5; color: #fff; padding: .85rem 2rem; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1rem; }
    .hero-cta:hover { background: #3730a3; }
    .price-callout { display: inline-flex; gap: 2rem; background: #f9f9f9; border: 1px solid #e5e5e5; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.25rem 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .price-callout .item { text-align: center; }
    .price-callout .item .price { font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 800; }
    .price-callout .item .label { font-size: 0.85rem; color: #777; margin-top: .2rem; }
    .price-callout .item.vouch .price { color: #4f46e5; }
    .price-callout .item.other .price { color: #dc2626; }
    section { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 3rem 2rem; }
    h2 { font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .compare-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .compare-table th { padding: .75rem 1rem; text-align: left; font-size: 0.85rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .05em; color: #888; border-bottom: 2px solid #eee; }
    .compare-table th:nth-child(2) { color: #4f46e5; }
    .compare-table td { padding: .85rem 1rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0; font-size: 0.97rem; vertical-align: top; }
    .compare-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
    .compare-table td:first-child { color: #555; font-weight: 500; }
    .yes { color: #16a34a; font-weight: 600; }
    .no { color: #dc2626; font-weight: 600; }
    .partial { color: #d97706; font-weight: 600; }
    .winner-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .winner-card { border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.75rem; }
    .winner-card.vouch { background: #f0fdf4; border: 1px solid #86efac; }
    .winner-card.other { background: #fafafa; border: 1px solid #e5e5e5; }
    .winner-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 800; margin: 0 0 .75rem; }
    .winner-card ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2rem; }
    .winner-card li { font-size: 0.92rem; color: #444; margin-bottom: .4rem; }
    .savings-box { background: #fffbeb; border: 1px solid #fcd34d; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.5rem 2rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .savings-box h3 { margin: 0 0 .5rem; font-size: 1rem; }
    .savings-box p { margin: 0; color: #555; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    .bottom-cta { text-align: center; background: #4f46e5; color: #fff; border-radius: 16px; padding: 3.5rem 2rem; margin: 3rem 0; }
    .bottom-cta h2 { color: #fff; margin-bottom: .75rem; }
    .bottom-cta p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); margin-bottom: 1.75rem; font-size: 1.05rem; }
    .bottom-cta a { display: inline-block; background: #fff; color: #4f46e5; padding: .85rem 2rem; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; }
    .bottom-cta a:hover { background: #e0e7ff; }
    footer { text-align: center; padding: 2rem; color: #999; font-size: 0.85rem; border-top: 1px solid #eee; }
    footer a { color: #999; margin: 0 .5rem; }
    @media (max-width: 600px) { .winner-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .price-callout { flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; } }
</style>
<nav>
  <a href="/" class="logo">SocialProof</a>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="/vs/fera">vs Fera</a>
    <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="cta-nav">Try Free</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<div class="hero">
  <span class="vs-badge">SocialProof vs Fera.ai</span>
  <h1>Fera is built for Shopify.<br/><span>SocialProof works everywhere.</span></h1>
  <p>Fera.ai is a Shopify-first social proof platform with order counts and product reviews. SocialProof focuses on what drives conversions most: genuine customer testimonials, collectible with one link, embeddable anywhere.</p>
  <div class="price-callout">
    <div class="item vouch"><div class="price">Free</div><div class="label">SocialProof starter</div></div>
    <div class="item other"><div class="price">$9+</div><div class="label">Fera.ai starter</div></div>
  </div>
  <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="hero-cta">Try SocialProof free →</a>
</div>

<section>
  <h2>Feature comparison</h2>
  <table class="compare-table">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Feature</th>
        <th>SocialProof</th>
        <th>Fera.ai</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td>Free tier</td><td class="yes">✓ Free forever (1 widget)</td><td class="partial">⚠ Free plan (very limited)</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Works on any website</td><td class="yes">✓ Any site — paste a script tag</td><td class="no">✗ Shopify-focused</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Collect testimonials via link</td><td class="yes">✓ Share a link, customer types it in</td><td class="partial">⚠ Post-purchase flow only</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Text testimonials</td><td class="yes">✓ Core feature</td><td class="partial">⚠ Review-style (stars + text)</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Embed widget</td><td class="yes">✓ Slider, grid, wall</td><td class="yes">✓ Multiple widget types</td></tr>
      <tr><td>No credit card to start</td><td class="yes">✓ Always</td><td class="partial">⚠ Card required for paid features</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Non-ecommerce businesses</td><td class="yes">✓ Coaches, consultants, services</td><td class="no">✗ Built for product stores</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Pro price</td><td class="yes">✓ $9/mo flat</td><td class="partial">⚠ $9–$99/mo based on orders</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Who should pick which?</h2>
  <div class="winner-grid">
    <div class="winner-card vouch">
      <h3>✅ SocialProof is best for...</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Service businesses, coaches, consultants, freelancers</li>
        <li>Any website that isn't a Shopify store</li>
        <li>Businesses that want to <strong>proactively collect</strong> testimonials via a shareable link</li>
        <li>Anyone who wants a simple, affordable, flat-rate tool</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="winner-card other">
      <h3>Fera.ai is best for...</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Shopify merchants who want integrated product reviews</li>
        <li>eCommerce stores that want "X people viewing this" and order-count widgets</li>
        <li>Brands that need review request emails built into their Shopify flow</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="savings-box">
    <h3>⚡ The key question: are you selling products or services?</h3>
    <p>Fera.ai is optimized for product-based eCommerce — Shopify order flows, review requests post-purchase, social proof counters. SocialProof is for any business that wants authentic customer testimonials and a clean way to display them. If you're a service business, SocialProof is the cleaner fit.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="bottom-cta">
    <h2>Start collecting testimonials free</h2>
    <p>No credit card. Works on Shopify, Webflow, Squarespace, WordPress, and more.</p>
    <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup">Get started free →</a>
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  <a href="/">SocialProof</a> · <a href="/vs/senja">vs Senja</a> · <a href="/vs/trustpilot">vs Trustpilot</a> · <a href="/vs/elfsight">vs Elfsight</a>
</footer>
</Base>
